  "title": "Preschool Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, supervise and implement the programme for the class in accordance with centre’s policies and framework</li>\n  <li>Complete progress reports on children for each semester and prepare a developmental portfolio for each child</li>\n  <li>Set up and create a stimulating and engaging pleasant learning environment that promotes self-directed learning</li>\n  <li>Responsible for all aspects of classroom management and carry out routine care duties to ensure safety and hygiene of the children</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the other teaching staff in the class in carrying out the duties</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain close partnership with parents</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma in Early Childhood Care and Education</li>\n  <li>Certified by ECDA at L2 category</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>High tolerance level towards children is an advantage</li>\n  <li>Able to work well independently as well as within a team</li>\n</ul>",
