    "description": "<p>Backed by 35 years of nurturing young minds and creating a strong foundation for countless children, The Schoolhouse by Busy Bees runs 14 preschools and 2 infant care centres in Singapore.<br>\n<br>\nBuilding on our renowned inquiry-embedded play based approach, our multiple literacies curriculum enriches each child’s understanding and connection with culture, society, environment, and technology to navigate the ever-changing world.<br>\n<br>\nExpect your children to be empowered with future ready skills and essential qualities like collaboration, creativity, critical thinking, and empathy to thrive in future communities and the world at large.</p>",
